\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\color blue
This is a nicely written paper showing how one may carry out Bayesian inference
 for the multivariate OU process.
 My one concern is that there is a fairly large literature on Bayesian inference
 for more general Gaussian Process models, and there is also some literature
 on connecting SPDE's to Gaussian processes.
 The lack of connection to this literature gives me pause at saying it should
 be published in PRE in its current form.
 I think the manuscript needs to connect to this wider literature and point
 out what the manuscript adds to the field.
\end_layout

